ued%20to%20workers%20involved%20in%20the%20WACA%20refurbishment%2C%20due%20to%20be%20completed%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20has%20the%20public%20been%20barred%20from%20watching%20India%20train%2C%20even%20those%20working%20in%20the%20precinct%20are%20under%20strict%20instructions%20not%20to%20take%20a%20peek%2C%20according%20to%20an%20email%20sent%20by%20Adam%20Sauzier%20of%20ADCO%20Constructions%2C%20who%20is%20building%20the%20new%20facility.%26quot%3B%20Quoting%20the%20e-mail%2C%20the%20newspaper%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20week%20India%20and%20India%20A%20are%20training%20at%20the%20WACA%20Ground%20from%20Tuesday%2012%20November%20until%20Sunday%2017%20November%2C%20as%20part%20of%20India's%20preparation%20for%20the%20Test%20Match%20at%20Perth%20Stadium%20the%20following%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20all%20training%20sessions%2C%20please%20do%20not%20take%20any%20photos%20or%20videos%20or%20fly%20any%20drones%2C%20of%20the%20training%20sessions%20and%20please%20do%20not%20sit%20and%20watch%20the%20sessions.%26quot%3B%20The%20leading%20daily%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20memo%20also%20makes%20reference%20to%20an%20India%20v%20India%20A%20match%20that%20had%20been%20scheduled%20from%20Friday%20to%20Sunday%20but%20has%20since%20been%20scrapped%20with%20the%20tourists%20instead%20preferring%20to%20have%20centre%20wicket%20practice.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20when%20people%20in%20the%20BCCI%20were%20asked%20they%20categorically%20denied%20having%20sent%20such%20official%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20from%20India%20or%20from%20India%20A%20such%20a%20request%2C%20at%20least%20on%20official%20capacity%2C%20has%20gone%20demanding%20closed-door%20net%20sessions.%20The%20practice%20session%20is%20open%20to%20all.%20The%20Indian%20and%20Australian%20media%20can%20watch%20and%20cover%20for%20as%20long%20as%20they%20want.%20There%20is%20no%20such%20restri