ecame%20the%20focus%20of%20local%20support.%20On%20November%2011%2C%202024%2C%20when%20they%20took%20their%20vehicle%20to%20Airport%20Marina%20Ford%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20for%20repair%2C%20the%20dealership%20surprised%20them%20with%20a%20brand-new%202023%20Ford%20Explorer%2C%20worth%20around%20%2436%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there's%20a%20child%20involved%20in%20a%20situation%20like%20that%2C%20and%20the%20condition%20of%20living%20in%20the%20other%20vehicle%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20survive%20out%20of%20that%2C%20and%20then%20that%20vehicle%20being%20as%20bad%20as%20it%20was%2C%20it%20was%20just%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dan%20Theroux%2C%20the%20general%20manager%20at%20Airport%20Marina%20Ford%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabc7.com%2Fpost%2Ffamily-boy-autism-was-slapped-man-viral-video-surprised-new-suv-la-ford-dealership%2F15528744%2F%5C%22%3E%20ABC%207.%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20explained%20that%20the%20Morales'%20old%20truck%20required%20costly%20replacements%2C%20including%20a%20new%20transmission%20and%20engine.%20The%20new%20SUV%20comes%20with%20a%20Gold%20Certified%20warranty%2C%20allowing%20the%20family%20to%20visit%20any%20Ford%20dealership%20for%20future%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamie%20Bishton%2C%20president%20of%20NOARUS%20Auto%20Group%2C%20shared%20that%20after%20inspecting%20the%20old%20truck%20on%20its%20arrival%2C%20they%20quickly%20recognised%20it%20needed%20more%20than%20just%20a%20few%20repairs.%20%E2%80%9CDan%20got%20the%20Ford%20to%20come%20into%20the%20dealership.%20We%20saw%20it%20on%20the%20flatbed%20and%20we%20were%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Uh%20oh%2C%20this%20needs%20more%20than%20just%20a%20repair%2C'%E2%80%9D%20Bishton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20incident%2C%20support%20has%20come%20from%20various%20quarters%2C%20including%20a%20GoFundMe%20campaign%20launched%20to%20help%20the%20family.%20The%20fundraiser's%20page%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlfredo%20was%20th