ting%20rights.%20The%20situation%20is%20tense%20as%20the%20tournament%20approaches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwatch-iccs-new-champions-trophy-promo-confirms-pakistan-as-host%2Farticleshow%2F115281034.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Poetry%20To%20UK%20Precedent%3A%20What%20Went%20Into%20Landmark%20'Bulldozer%20Justice'%20Verdict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20judgment%20yesterday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20demolished%20the%20idea%20of%20'bulldozer%20justice'%20that%20several%20state%20governments%20had%20unleashed%20against%20accused%20in%20heinous%20criminal%20cases.%C2%A0The%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20KV%20Viswanathan%20took%20a%20tough%20stand%20against%20such%20actions%2C%20holding%20that%20the%20Executive%20cannot%20cannot%20replace%20the%20Judiciary%20and%20the%20legal%20process%20should%20not%20prejudge%20the%20guilt%20of%20an%20accused.%20But%20laws%2C%20precedents%20and%20doctrines%20aside%2C%20it%20was%20idea%20of%20'home'%20that%20was%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2095-page%20order%20started%20with%20four%20lines%20of%20a%20Hindi%20poem%20by%20Kavi%20Pradeep%2C%20who%20penned%20the%20timeless%20%26quot%3BAye%20Mere%20Watan%20Ke%20Logon%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20tribute%20to%20soldiers%20killed%20in%20the%201962%20Sino-Indian%20War.%20The%20four%20lines%20in%20the%20court's%20order%20were%3A%20%26quot%3BApna%20ghar%20ho%2C%20apna%20aangan%20ho%2C%20is%20khwab%20mein%20har%20koi%20jita%20hai%2C%20insaan%20ke%20dil%20ki%20yeh%20chahat%20hai%2C%20ki%20ek%20ghar%20ka%20sapna%20kabhi%20na%20chute%26quot%3B.%20The%20lines%20roughly%20translate%20to%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20everyone's%20dream%20to%20have%20a%20home%2C%20a%20courtyard.%20No%20one%20wants%20to%20lose%20the%20dream%20for%20a%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20in%20its%20order%20that%20for%20an%20average%20citizen%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20house%20is%20often%20the%20culmination%20of%20years%20of%20hard%C2%A0work%2C%20dreams%2C%20and%20aspirations.%20%26quot%3BA%20house%20is%20not%20just%20a%20property%20but%20embodies%20the%20collective%20hopes%20of%20a%20family%20or%20individuals%20for%20stability%2C%20security%2C%20and%20a%20future.%20Having%20a%20house%20or%20a%20roof%20over%20one's%20head%20gives%20satisfaction%20to%20any%20person.%20It%20gives%20a%20sense%20of%20dignity%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging.%20If%20this%20is%20to%20be%20taken%20away%2C%20then%20the%20authority%20must%20be%20satisfied%20that%20this%20is%20the%20only%20option%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Ft5loqob8_bulldozer-justice-judges_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20KV%20Viswanathan%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Work%20Behind%20The%20Judgment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20judgments%20and%20observations%20run%20as%20short%20breaking%20news%20flashes%20and%20social%20media%20posts.%20But%20these%20do%20not%20wholly%20encapsulate%20the%20hard%20work%20that%20goes%20into%20penning%20these%20orders.%20It%20took%20Justice%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20Viswanathan%2044%20days%20to%20prepare%20this%2095-page%20judgment%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%20The%20sources%20said%20the%20two%20judges%20held%20several%20meetings%20and%20decided%20that%20this%20judgment%20would%20have%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20crores%20of%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20from%20underprivileged%20sections%20that%20are%20powerless%20before%20the%20might%20of%20the%20State%20and%20excesses%20such%20as%20'bulldozer%20justice'.%20So%20the%20judgment%2C%20the%20judges%20agreed%2C%20must%20be%20written%20in%20a%20way%20that%20reaches%20and%20connects%20with%20the%20common%20citizen%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gavai%2C%20who%20is%20the%20next%20in%20line%20for%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20post%2C%20sat%20hours%20looking%20for%20a%20poem%20that%20resonates%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20'shelter'%20that%20the%20judges%20wanted%20to%20capture%20in%20the%20order%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20found%20the%20lines%20by%20Pradeep%20that%20opened%20the%20key%20judgment.%20The%20lines%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20judgment%20that%20stressed%20on%20the%20right%20to%20shelter%20and%20summed%20up%20that%20this%20was%20not%20a%20case%20about%20structures%20and%20their%20legality%2C%20but%20the%20people%20living%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Precedents%20-%20And%20Lord%20Denning's%20Lines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20idea%20of%20'home'%20was%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20judgment%2C%20its%20brain%20was%20backed%20by%20legal%20precedents%20and%20landmark%20verdicts.%20The%20judges%20included%20an%20observation%20by%20British%20judge%20Lord%20Denning%2C%20who%20Margaret%20Thatcher%20had%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20the%20greatest%20English%20judge%20of%20modern%20times%26quot%3B.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20judgments%2C%20Lord%20Denning%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20poorest%20man%20may%20in%20his%20cottage%20bid%20defiance%20to%20all%20the%20forces%20of%20the%20Crown.%20It%20may%20be%20frail%20-%20its%20roof%20may%20shake%20-%20the%20wind%20may%20blow%20through%20it%20-%20the%20storm%20may%20enter%20-%20the%20rain%20may%20enter%20-%20but%20the%20King%20of%20England%20cannot%20enter%20-%20all%20his%20force%20dares%20not%20cross%20the%20threshold%20of%20the%20ruined%20tenement.'%20So%20be%20it%20-%20unless%20he%20has%20justification%20by%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lines%20reflected%20the%20bench's%20view%20on%20the%20State's%20right%20to%20deprive%20a%20family%20of%20its%20shelter%20as%20a%20penalty%20against%20someone%20accused%20of%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20later%20noted%20in%20its%20judgment%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20chilling%20sight%20of%20a%20bulldozer%20demolishing%20a%20building%2C%20when%20authorities%20have%20failed%20to%20follow%20the%20basic%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%20and%20have%20acted%20without%20adhering%20to%20the%20principle%20of%20due%20process%2C%20reminds%20one%20of%20a%20lawless%20state%20of%20affairs%2C%20where%20'might%20was%20right'%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20such%20%26quot%3Bhigh-handed%20and%20arbitrary%20actions%26quot%3B%20have%20no%20place%20in%20our%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20judgments%20the%20court%20referred%20to%20included%20the%20Raj%20Narain%20vs%20Indira%20Gandhi%20case%2C%20the%20Bilkis%20Bano%20case%20and%20the%20Aadhaar%20verdict.%20The%20judges%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20researched%20for%20over%20a%20month%20as%20they%20prepared%20the%20order%20that%20dealt%20with%20the%20separation%20of%20powers%2C%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20the%20rights%20of%20accused%2C%20right%20to%20shelter%20and%20accountability%20of%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20agreed%20that%20the%20order%20must%20be%20penned%20in%20a%20manner%20so%20that%20the%20court's%20direction%20do%20not%20just%20remain%20on%20paper%2C%20but%20are%20applied%20on%20the%20ground.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20Justice%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20Viswanathan%20were%20of%20the%20view%20that%20this%20verdict%20would%20impact%20lives%20of%20those%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20social%20pyramid%20and%20they%20must%20have%20adequate%20safeguards%20against%20arbitrary%20actions%20by%20the%20State.%20This%20formed%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20judgment%20laying%20down%20that%20officers%20found%20to%20violate%20the%20top%20court's%20guidelines%20on%20demolition%20would%20face%20contempt%20proceedings.%20They%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20damages%20and%20restore%20the%20property%20at%20their%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731561900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fch7ohea8_supreme-court-bulldozer-split_625x300_22_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-justice-br-gavai-justice-kv-viswanathan-poetry-to-uk-precedent-what-went-into-landmark-bulldozer-justice-verdict-7015731%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20landmark%20judgment%20yesterday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20demolished%20the%20idea%20of%20'bulldozer%20justice'%20that%20several%20state%20governments%20had%20unleashed%20against%20accused%20in%20heinous%20criminal%20cases.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-justice-br-gavai-justice-kv-viswanathan-poetry-to-uk-precedent-what-went-into-landmark-bulldozer-justice-verdict-7015731%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jio%20Fin%2C%20Zomato%2C%20Angel%20One%2C%20Paytm%20rally%20up%20to%207%25%20on%20inclusion%20in%20F%26amp%3BO%20pool%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731561890000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fjio-financial-zomato-angel-one-paytm-rally-up-to-7-on-inclusion-in-f-o-124111400478_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20exchanges%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20the%20addition%20of%2045%20stocks%20to%20the%20new%20list%20of%20scrips%20eligible%20for%20trading%20in%20the%20F%26amp%3BO%20segment%20from%20November%2029.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhat%20A%20Father%20Would...%26quot%3B%3A%20On%20Rohit's%20Availability%20vs%20Aus%