with%20pushing%20Ashtanga%20yoga%20to%20mainstream%20popularity%2C%20Mr%20Jois%20is%20known%20for%20memorialising%20his%20legacy%20following%20his%20grandfather's%20death%20in%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Falexei-zimin-a-uk-based-russian-chef-who-criticised-vladimir-putin-found-dead-in-serbia-hotel-7014924%5C%22%3EAlexei%20Zimin%2C%20A%20UK-Based%20Russian%20Chef%20Who%20Criticised%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20Found%20Dead%20In%20Serbia%20Hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20his%20death%2C%20Mr%20Jois%20had%20taught%20a%20low-intensity%20version%20of%20Ashtanga%20yoga%20that%20he%20had%20recently%20developed%2C%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BActive%20Series%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20instructors%20from%20around%20the%20world%20at%20a%20seminar%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia.%20That%20afternoon%2C%20he%20went%20on%20a%20hike%20with%20around%2050%20students.%20Appearing%20fatigued%2C%20Mr%20Jois%20was%20trailing%20the%20group%20when%20he%20sat%20on%20a%20bench%20about%20a%20third%20of%20a%20mile%20into%20the%20trail%2C%20and%20later%20fell%20off%20it%2C%20John%20Bultman%2C%20the%20yoga%20program%20manager%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents'%20attempts%20to%20revive%20him%20using%20CPR%20failed%2C%20and%20he%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20moments%20after%20emergency%20medical%20workers%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharath%20Jois%20was%20born%20Rangaswamy%20Sharath%20on%20September%2029%2C%201971%2C%20in%20Mysore.%20Besides%20his%20sister%2C%20he%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20mother%2C%20Saraswathi%20Jois%2C%20father%20Rangaswamy%2C%20wife%20Shruti%20Jois%2C%20and%20two%20children%2C%20son%20Sambhav%20Jois%20and%20daughter%20Shraddha%20Jois.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731559800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F4s