%2F21142056%2Fschool-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20nation%20celebrates%20Children's%20Day%2C%20can%20we%20look%20a%20child%20in%20the%20eye%20and%20say%3A%20%E2%80%98Happy%20Children's%20Day'.%20Have%20we%20let%20the%20kids%20of%20our%20nation%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20had%20sanctioned%20an%20Eklavya%20school%20near%2011-year-old%20Sulekha's%20home.%20Today%2C%20Sulekha%20is%2016.%20The%20school%20in%20her%20neighbourhood%20is%20still%20not%20functional.%20This%20is%20true%20for%20two%20out%20of%20five%20schools%20sanctioned%20under%20the%20Eklavya%20Model%20Residential%20School%20scheme.%20Sulekha%20is%20forced%20to%20enrol%20in%20the%20Kasturba%20Gandhi%20Balika%20Vidyalaya%20(KGBV)%20located%20in%20an%20%E2%80%98educationally%20backward%20area'.%20Her%20favourite%20class%20isn't%20held%20because%20the%20teacher's%20position%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20filled%20by%20the%20administration%20that%20reports%20to%20the%20Union%20government.%20As%20of%20July%202024%2C%20there%20are%20over%204%2C000%20teacher%20vacancies%20in%20KGBVs.%20The%20highest%20vacancies%20are%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Even%20for%20subjects%20with%20assigned%20teachers%2C%20classes%20do%20not%20take%20place%20daily%E2%80%94teachers%20are%20frequently%20absent.%20It%20is%20common%20practice%20that%20even%20for%20a%20five-day%20week%2C%20teachers%20take%20an%20extra%20day%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Grim%20Childhood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESulekha%20is%20in%20class%2010%20now.%20She%20struggles%20to%20read%20texts%20of%20what%20a%20student%20in%20class%202%20should%20know.%20She%20is%20unable%20to%20solve%20maths%20problems%20that%20are%20from%20the%20class%203%20level.%20One%20out%20of%20four%20rural%20youth%2C%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2014%20to%2018%2C%20demonstrate%20a%20similar%20gap%20in%20learning.%20Research%20suggests%20that%20half%20the%20students%20in%20this%20age%20group%20are%20unable%20to%20solve%20arithmetic%20that%20is%20taught%20in%20class%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20support%20her%20family%2C%20Sulekha%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school.%20One%20in%20every%20five%20students%20is%20compelled%20to%20do%20so.%20As%20an%20alternative%20to%20school%20education%2C%20she%20then%20enrols%20herself%20in%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Kaushal%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(PMKVY)%E2%80%94a%20%E2%80%9Cflagship%E2%80%9D%20scheme%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20launched%20to%20upskill%20youth%20in%20order%20to%20improve%20the%20employment%20opportunities%20available%20to%20them.%20Sulekha%20completes%20all%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20programme.%20She%20is%20even%20awarded%20with%20a%20certificate.%20But%20nothing%20changes.%20Like%20half%20of%20the%20certificate%20holders%2C%20she%20finds%20no%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoping%20with%20all%20this%20pressure%20at%20a%20young%20age%20can%20be%20traumatic.%20On%20paper%2C%20teenagers%20with%20mental%20health%20issues%20can%20seek%20help%20through%20Manodarpan%2C%20a%20mental%20health%20support%20helpline%20launched%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20A%20good%20idea%20but%20poorly%20implemented.%20Calls%20to%20the%20helpline%20(844%20844%200632)%20almost%20always%20go%20unanswered.%20There%20are%20just%20366%20counsellors%20listed%20in%20Manodarpan's%20directory%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20District%20Mental%20Health%20Programme%20is%20no%20better.%20Just%201%2C178%20psychiatrists%20and%20513%20trained%20psychologists%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThousands%20Of%20Sulekhas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESulekha's%20story%20is%20not%20a%20one-off.%20It%20is%20the%20story%20of%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20youngsters%20in%20India.%20Thirty-five%20students%20commit%20suicide%20every%20day%20(the%20actual%20numbers%20could%20be%20even%20higher).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20such%20students%20depend%20on%20schemes%20like%20Samagra%20Shiksha%2C%20which%20provides%20for%20teacher%20salaries%2C%20fees%20for%20those%20enrolled%20under%20Right%20To%20Education%2C%20uniforms%20and%20school%20infrastructure.%20However%2C%20the%20funds%20under%20the%20scheme%20for%20states%20ruled%20by%20non-BJP%20parties%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Punjab%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Delhi%20have%20either%20been%20stalled%20or%20denied.%20Why%3F%20Is%20it%20because%20they%20objected%20to%20a%20certain%20suffix%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20scheme%3F%20The%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%20advocates%20for%20an%20allocation%20of%206%25%20of%20the%20GDP%20to%20education.%20Good%20intentions%2C%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20a%20mirage.%20In%202023-24%2C%20the%20Union%20allocated%200.44%25%20of%20GDP%20to%20education.%20This%20was%20reduced%20to%200.37%25%20in%20this%20year's%20Budget.%20Sorry%20Sulekha%2C%20we%20failed%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EResearch%20credit%3A%20Dheemunt%20Jain%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731556620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw.ndtvimg.com%2Fsites%2F3%2F2023%2F07%2F21142056%2Fschool-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-is-failing-its-young-but-happy-childrens-day-i-guess-7015158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20support%20her%20family%2C%20Sulekha%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school.%20One%20in%20every%20five%20students%20is%20compelled%20to%20do%20so.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-is-failing-its-young-but-happy-childrens-day-i-guess-7015158%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Republicans%20