agement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-contractor-to-pay-42-million-to-3-iraqis-tortured-at-baghdad-prison-7005241%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK-Based%20Russian%20Chef%20Who%20Criticised%20Putin%20Found%20Dead%20In%20Serbia%20Hotel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Russian%20television%20chef%2C%20who%20was%20an%20outspoken%20critic%20of%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20has%20been%20found%20dead%20in%20Serbia%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%20Alexei%20Zimin%2C%2052%2C%20was%20considered%20a%20household%20name%20in%20Russia%20before%20he%20left%20the%20country%20after%20criticising%20the%20Kremlin's%20annexation%20of%20Crimea%20in%202014.%20He%20set%20up%20his%20new%20home%20and%20businesses%20in%20London%20but%20remained%20the%20host%20of%20a%20popular%20cookery%20show%20on%20Russian%20broadcaster%20NTV.%20However%2C%20the%20show%20was%20axed%20after%20he%20posted%20an%20anti-war%20message%20on%20social%20media%20following%20the%20full-scale%20Russian%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Zimin%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20a%20hotel%20room%20in%20Belgrade%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc7049jn5kd3o%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported%20citing%20Russian%20media.%20He%20had%20travelled%20to%20the%20Serbian%20capital%20to%20promote%20his%20new%20book%20about%20Britain%20Anglomania.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESerbian%20authorities%20have%20said%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bno%20suspicious%20circumstances%26quot%3B%20related%20to%20Mr%20Zimin's%20death%20and%20that%20an%20autopsy%20and%20toxicology%20report%20was%20ongoing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaterina%20Ternovskaya%2C%20co-owner%20of%20the%20restaurant%20where%20the%2052-year-old%20had%20presented%20his%20book%2C%20said%20people%20were%20%26qu