tt%20Gaetz%20as%20his%20pick%20for%20attorney%20general.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGaetz%20has%20criticized%20Big%20Tech%20for%20censoring%20conservatives%20and%20supports%20antitrust%20enforcement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBoth%20the%20Justice%20Department%20and%20the%20FTC%20enforce%20antitrust%20laws%20that%20impact%20large%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-nominates-matt-gaetz-attorney-general-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enamed%20Rep.%20Matt%20Gaetz%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20his%20pick%20for%20attorney%20general%2C%20an%20appointment%20which%2C%20if%20approved%20by%20the%20Senate%2C%20would%20give%20the%20Florida%20Republican%20sweeping%20legal%20power%20and%20the%20opportunity%20to%20act%20on%20his%20longstanding%20complaints%20against%20Big%20Tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaetz%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatt-gaetz-says-american-obligation-take-up-arms-big-tech-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrequently%20railed%20against%20Big%20Tech%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accusing%20Silicon%20Valley%20firms%20of%20censoring%20conservatives%2C%20and%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20he%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20fierce%20advocate%20for%20antitrust%20enforcement%2C%20particularly%20against%20companies%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Alphabet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20internet's%20hall%20monitors%20out%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20they%20think%20they%20can%20suppress%20us%2C%20discourage%20us.%20Maybe%20if%20you're%20just%20a%20little%20less%20patriotic.%20Maybe%20if%20you%20just%20conform%20to%20their%20way%20of%20thinking%20a%20little%20more%2C%20then%20you'll%20be%20allowed%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20digital%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaetz%20said%20during%20a%202021%20appearance%20shortly%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-trump-bans-from-twitter-facebook-dont-violate-first-amendment-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20had%20been%20banned%20from%20social%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-trump-bans-from-twitter-facebook-dont-violate-first-amendment-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedia%20platforms%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20January%206%20insurrection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20you%20know%20what%3F%20Silicon%20Valley%20can't%20cancel%20this%20movement%2C%20or%20this%20rally%2C%20or%20this%20congressman%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20audience.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20Second%20Amendment%20in%20this%20country%2C%20and%20I%20think%20we%20have%20an%20obligation%20to%20use%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20unclear%20how%20much%20his%20appointment%20to%20attorney%20general%2C%20if%20approved%20by%20the%20Senate%2C%20would%20impact%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20the%20congressman%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Justice%20Department%20and%20the%20FTC%20are%20responsible%20for%20enforcing%20antitrust%20laws%20in%20the%20US.%20Current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftc-chair-lina-khan-60-minutes-americans-privacy-big-tech-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Trade%20Commission%20chair%20Lina%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20Trump%20may%20end%20up%20replacing%2C%20has%20been%20aggressive%20at%20going%20after%20Big%20Tech%20companies.%20Khan%20has%20worked%20to%20stifle%20billions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20deals%20over%20anti-competitive%20concerns%2C%20and%20the%20FTC%20has%20brought%20lawsuits%20against%20Nvidia%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20work%20puts%20her%20somewhat%20in%20alignment%20with%20Gaetz%20and%20Vice%20President-elect%20JD%20Vance%2C%20who%20has%20praised%20her%20work.%20Gaetz%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpolicy%2Flina-khan-ftc-antitrust-khanservatives-a6852a8f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%20that%20he%20hopes%20%26quot%3Bwhoever%20is%20the%20next%20FTC%20chair%20would%20continue%20many%20of%20the%20cases%20that%20Chair%20Khan%20has%20brought%20against%20predatory%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20although%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faoc-brawl-harris-lina-khan-ftc-mark-cuban-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKhan%20could%20be%20departing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20possible%20the%20federal%20government's%20antitrust%20policy%20towards%20major%20tech%20companies%20does%20not%20drastically%20change%2C%20according%20to%20Mark%20A.%20Kasten%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20Buchanan%20Ingersoll%20and%20Rooney%20focusing%20on%20white-collar%20criminal%20defense%2C%20compliance%2C%20and%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20also%20depend%20on%20who%20Trump%20picks%20to%20chair%20the%20FTC.%20Though%20he%20is%20expected%20to%20fire%20Khan%2C%20it's%20unclear%20who%20he%20would%20tap%20to%20lead%20the%20agency%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20we%20still%20expect%20to%20see%20a%20meaningful%20uptick%20in%20M%26amp%3BA%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaac%20Boltansky%2C%20BTIG's%20director%20of%20policy%20research%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barrons.com%2Farticles%2Fmatt-gaetz-trump-pick-attorney-general-226abe2a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarron's%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Gaetz%20was%20nominated%2C%20referring%20to%20mergers%20an%20acquisitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20hurdles%20for%20Big%20Tech%20could%20remain%20elevated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKasten%2C%20who%20has%20defended%20clients%20who%20were%20under%20investigation%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department%2C%20also%20noted%20that%20Gaetz%20voted%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-app-american-us-not-worried-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%20ban%20passed%20in%20April%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20bill%2C%20aimed%20at%20beefing%20up%20national%20security%20against%20China%2C%20requires%20the%20app's%20Chinese%20owner%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20to%20sell%20its%20US%20assets%20by%20January%20or%20be%20banned%20from%20app%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20that%20law%20passed%2C%20and%20requires%20the%20platform%20to%20be%20sold%20to%20a%20non-Chinese%20company%20in%20January%2C%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20see%20a%20world%20in%20which%20an%20Attorney%20General%20Gaetz%20doesn't%20enforce%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Kasten%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20vote%2C%20Gaetz%20said%20he%20believed%20banning%20TikTok%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20idea%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20he%20took%20issue%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Boverly%20broad%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Brushed%26quot%3B%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20no%20way%20to%20run%20a%20railroad%20(or%20the%20internet)%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaetz%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-coporate-monopolies-antitrust-lawsuits-live-nation-amazon-google-meta-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20tech%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20Apple%2C%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Amazon%2C%20are%20already%20contending%20with%20antitrust%20cases%20filed%20over%20the%20last%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Hay%2C%20an%20antitrust%20expert%20and%20law%20professor%20at%20Cornell%20University%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20incoming%20presidents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-presidency-affect-big-tech-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egenerally%20don't%20alter%20current%20cases.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20rare%20that%2C%20at%20the%20presidential%20level%2C%20there's%20any%20attempt%20to%20influence%20the%20course%20of%20cases%20which%20have%20already%20been%20filed.%20Those%20have%20a%20life%20of%20their%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20Hay%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20depend%20on%20the%20judge%2C%20the%20courts%2C%20the%20lawyers%20who%20carry%20on%20a%20case.%20It's%20extraordinarily%20unusual%20for%20the%20administration%20to%20become%20at%20all%20active.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatt-gaetz-criticism-big-tech-trump-attorney-general-antitrust-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731552834000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673555b3ede4eeae39275a39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatt-gaetz-criticism-big-tech-trump-attorney-general-antitrust-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Matt%20Gaetz%20has%20railed%20against%20Big%20Tech%20companies.%20If%20he%20becomes%20Trump's%20attorney%20general%2C%20he'd%20have%20legal%20power%20to%20act%20on%20his%20complaints.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40businessinsider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass%2CKelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatt-gaetz-criticism-big-tech-trump-attorney-general-antitrust-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SKY%20Reveals%20'Sacrifice'%20For%20Tilak%20That%20Worked%20Wonders%20For%20India%20Against%20SA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20victory%20over%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20third%20T20I%20match%2C%20India%20skipper%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20said%20that%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20have%20played%20the%20brand%20of%20cricket%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20play.%20India%20clinched%20an%2011-run%20victory%20over%20South%20Africa%20in%20Centurion.%20With%20a%20thrilling%20victory%20in%20Centurion%2C%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20took%20a%202-1%20lead%20in%20the%20four-match%20T20I%20series.%20The%20India%20skipper%20failed%20to%20shine%20in%20the%20game%20as%20he%20scored%20just%20one%20run%20from%20four%20balls%20in%20the%20first%20inning.%20His%20time%20on%20the%20crease%20came%20to%20an%20end%20after%20Andile%20Simelane%20removed%20him.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation%2C%20Suryakumar%20spoke%20about%20the%20youngsters%20in%20the%20squad%20and%20said%20that%20even%20if%20they%20miss%20out%20in%20a%20few%20innings%2C%20they%20back%20their%20intent%20and%20their%20game%20to%20make%20a%20comeback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20skipper%20also%20showered%20praise%20on%20Tilak%20Varma%20and%20said%20that%20the%20youngster%20was%20capable%20of%20doing%20what%20he%20did%20in%20Centurion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20happy.%20What%20we%20spoke%20about%20in%20the%20team%20meetings%2C%20we%20played%20the%20brand%20of%20cricket%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20play.%20(How%20the%20young%20players%20take%20on%20the%20message%20of%20being%20fearless)%20That%20is%20what%20we%20have%20been%20telling%20them%20to%20do%20-%20similar%20to%20what%20they%20have%20been%20doing%20in%20the%20nets%2C%20for%20their%20franchises%20and%20for%20their%20states.%20Even%20if%20they%20miss%20out%20in%20a%20few%20innings%2C%20they%20back%20their%20intent%20and%20their%20game...%20And%20what%20can%20I%20say%20about%20Tilak%20Varma.%20He%20came%20to%20me%20(in%20Gqeberha)%2C%20asked%20me%20if%20he%20could%20bat%20at%20three.%20I%20said%20to%20him%20it%20was%20his%20day%20and%20to%20enjoy%20himself.%20I%20knew%20what%20he%20was%20capable%20of%20doing%20and%20very%20happy%20for%20him.%20He%20is%20batting%20at%20three%20going%20forward%20definitely%20(smiles).%20He%20asked%20for%20it%2C%20he%20delivered.%20Very%20happy%20for%20his%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Suryakumar%20was%20quoted%20by%20ESPNcricinfo%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecapping%20the%20match%2C%20South%20Africa%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20decided%20to%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20Sharma%20(50%20runs%20from%2025%20balls%2C%203%20fours%20and%205%20sixes)%20and%20Tilak%20Varma%20(107*%20runs%20from%2056%20balls%2C%208%20fours%20and%207%20sixes)%20displayed%20a%20stupendous%20knock%20and%20powered%20India%20to%20219%2F6%20in%20the%20first%20inning.%20Other%20Men%20in%20Blue%20batters%20failed%20to%20shine%20with%20the%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndile%20Simelane%20and%20Keshav%20Maharaj%20led%20the%20Proteas%20bowling%20attack%20as%20they%20bagged%20two%20wickets%20each%20in%20their%20respective%20spell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20run%20chase%2C%20Heinrich%20Klaasen%20(41%20runs%20from%2022%20balls%2C%201%20four%20and%204%20sixes)%20and%20Marco%20Jansen%20(54%20runs%20from%2017%20balls%2C%204%20fours%20and%205%20sixes)%20played%20a%20blitzkrieg%20knock%20and%20kept%20the%20Proteas%20in%20the%20game.%20But%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Arshdeep%2C%20it%20was%20India%20who%20smiled%20in%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshdeep%20Singh%20did%20the%20job%20both%20with%20the%20new%20ball%20and%20in%20the%20death%20overs%20as%20he%20picked%20up%20three%20crucial%20wickets%20and%20gave%2037%20runs%20in%20his%20four-over%20spell.%20Varun%20Chakaravarthy%20bagged%20two%20wickets%20in%20his%20four-over%20spell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETilak%20Varma%20was%20named%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20following%20his%20staggering%20performance%20with%20the%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731552180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fheq3uks8_sc_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2024%2Fsuryakumar-yadav-reveals-sacrifice-for-tilak-varma-that-worked-wonders-for-india-against-south-africa-7013801%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%20showered%20praise%20on%20Tilak%20Varma%20and%20said%20that%20the%20youngster%20was%20capable%20of%20doing%20what%20he%20did%20in%20Centurion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22e