certain%20future.%20The%20BCCI%2C%20after%20not%20receiving%20clearance%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20has%20informed%20the%20International%20Cricket%20%C2%A0Council%20(ICC)%20that%20it%20will%20not%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%202025.%20The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%2C%20the%20designated%20host%2C%20is%20adamant%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20hybrid%20model%20where%20India%20play%20its%20matches%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue.%20The%20PCB%20has%20also%20shot%20off%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20ICC%20asking%20the%20world%20body%20to%20give%20in%20writing%20its%20and%20BCCI's%20stance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20last%20played%20a%20bilateral%20series%20in%202012-13.%20Since%20then%2C%20they%20have%20played%20each%20other%20only%20in%20ICC%20and%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20events.%20The%202023%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20where%20Pakistan%20were%20the%20hosts%2C%20saw%20a%20hybrid%20model%20where%20India%20played%20its%20matches%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cricbuzz.com%2Fcricket-news%2F132398%2Ficc-in-a-catch-22-situation-amid-pcbs-steadfast-stance-on-hosting-champions-trophy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20if%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20continues%20to%20maintain%20its%20tough%20stance%20and%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20gets%20affected%20it%20may%20result%20in%20sanctions%20from%20the%20ICC.%20If%20PCB%20withdraw%2C%20its%20ICC%20funding%20can%20be%20cut%20substantially.%20Moving%20or%20postponing%20the%20tournament%20could%20mean%20PCB%20losing%20out%20on%20approximately%20USD%2065%20million%20as%20host%20fees.%20Recently%20the%20PCB%20upgraded%20three%20venues%20-%20Karachi%2C%20Rawalpindi%2C%20and%20Lahore%20-%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20and%20any%20financial%20loss%20would%20hurt%20them%20even%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20has%20conveyed%20to%20the%20ICC%20that%20security%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20in%20the%20country%20which%20successfully%20hosted%20England%20and%20New%20Zealand%20recently%20and%20promised%20the%20same%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remained%20steadfast%20on%20its%20stand%20to%20not%20have%20the%20event%20in%20hybrid%20model%2C%20like%20the%20last%20year's%20Asia%20Cup%20when%20India's%20matches%20were%20held%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20PCB%20and%20was%20discussing%20the%20schedule%20with%20the%20participating%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20agency%20PTI%20has%20learned%20that%20the%20PCB%20is%20also%20not%20keen%20to%20host%20the%20tournament%20outside%20the%20country%2C%20not%20even%20in%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%20the%20launch%20event%20in%20Lahore%20has%20been%20pushed%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20being%20planned%20in%20Lahore%20as%20per%20ICC%20management's%20briefing%20to%20the%20ICC%20CEC%20and%20ICC%20Board%20on%2021st%20October%20in%20Dubai.%20But%20this%20has%20now%20been%20put%20on%20a%20hold%2C%20informed%20an%20ICC%20insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731549000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-10%2Flm5mljg8_india-pakistan-match-afp_640x480_24_October_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2F65-million-icc-sanctions-and-pakistan-cricket-board-faces-severe-loss-if-champions-trophy-row-escalates-7010445%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20PCB%20has%20conveyed%20to%20the%20ICC%20that%20security%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20in%20the%20country%20which%20successfully%20hosted%20England%20and%20New%20Zealand%20recently%20and%20promised%20the%20same%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2F65-million-icc-sanctions-and-pakistan-cricket-board-faces-severe-loss-i