3ESince%20winning%20his%20senate%20seat%20in%202010%2C%20Rubio%20has%20been%20an%20outspoken%20critic%20of%20China.%20He's%20repeatedly%20spoken%20out%20about%20China's%20ambitious%20military%20and%20political%20goals%2C%20economic%20power%2C%20and%20the%20US'%20response%20to%20its%20growing%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Beijing%20has%20taken%20note.%20In%202020%2C%20Rubio%20and%20other%20US%20Senators%20were%20sanctioned%20by%20Beijing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-53722811%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERubio%20was%20sanctioned%2C%20or%20blacklisted%2C%20twice%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20first%20in%20retaliation%20for%20US%20measures%20against%20senior%20Chinese%20officials%20over%20the%20mass%20detainment%20and%20abuse%20of%20the%20Uyghur%20ethnic%20group%2C%20and%20the%20second%20after%20Rubio%20supported%20US%20sanctions%20against%20Chinese%20officials%20for%20their%20response%20to%20protests%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20Rubio%20has%20accused%20China%20of%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bgrotesque%20campaign%20of%20genocide%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20Uyghurs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20now%20is%20whether%20China%20will%20lift%20the%20sanctions%20on%20Rubio%2C%20which%20may%20prohibit%20him%20from%20traveling%20to%20the%20country%2C%20and%20how%20Washington's%20relations%20with%20Beijing%20could%20be%20impacted%20if%20Rubio's%20confirmed.%20But%20China's%20actions%20haven't%20stopped%20Rubio%20from%20continuing%20to%20speak%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%202022%20talk%20with%20The%20Heritage%20Foundation%2C%20Rubio%20said%20members%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20had%2C%20for%20decades%2C%20%26quot%3Bhid%20their%20true%20ambition%20to%20remake%20the%20global%20order%20and%20become%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20nation.%20But%20they%20don't%20hide%20it%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20and%20top%20China%20watchers%20have%20indicated%20that%20China's%20goals%2C%20along%20with%20t