0the%20ideal%20environments%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20explore%20new%20ideas.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20aim%20to%20do%20through%20our%20thingQbator%20programme%20%E2%80%93%20we%20collaborate%20with%20universities%20to%20identify%20and%20mentor%20young%20minds%2C%20helping%20them%20shape%20and%20realize%20their%20entrepreneurial%20aspirations.%20This%20initiative%20is%20not%20just%20about%20nurturing%20startups%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20empowering%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20innovators%20to%20create%20impactful%20solutions%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Harish%20Krishnan%2C%20Managing%20Director%20%26amp%3B%20Chief%20Policy%20Officer%2C%20Cisco%20India%20%26amp%3B%20SAARC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%20%26amp%3B%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20nasscom%20foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731321261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D378406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20thingQbator%20programme%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Cisco%20and%20nasscom%20foundation%20initiative%20%E2%80%94%20nurtures%20young%20innovators%20by%20providing%20mentorship%2C%20funding%2C%20and%20resources%20to%20solve%20societal%20issues%20using%20technology.%20Since%202018%2C%20it%20has%20incubated%20over%2058%20startups%2C%20addressing%20challenges%20in%20education%2C%20agriculture%2C%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20accessibility%2C%20empowering%20students%20to%20become%20job%20creators%20and%20future-ready%20entrepreneurs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F378406%2Fnasscom-foundation-cisco-thingqbator-startups-mentorship-funding-solve-social-issues-using-technology%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Inside%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Sustainable%20Home%20With%20No%20Water%2C%20Gas%2C%20or%20Electricity%20Connecti