0artists%2C%20singing%20with%20heads%20held%20high%2C%20are%20not%20performing%20for%20the%20audience%2C%20but%20singing%20directly%20to%20a%20higher%20power%20in%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20only%20took%20one%20Shri%20Ravi%20Shankar%20%3Cem%3Eji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20extend%20the%20sitar%E2%80%99s%20influence%20for%20another%20century.%20Similarly%2C%20it%20will%20only%20take%20a%20few%20properly%20trained%20and%20passionate%20young%20people%20to%20revive%20the%20rich%20music%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20ensure%20its%20survival%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20assures%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Govind%20Singh%20Bhati%20and%20Sharon%20Genevive%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731072652000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8733_11zon-1731069402.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D375518%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20world%20where%20traditional%20art%20forms%20are%20fading%20away%2C%20Govind%20Singh%20Bhati%20and%20Sharon%20Genevive%20are%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20revive%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20folk%20musical%20heritage.%20Through%20their%20one%20of%20a%20kind%20programme%2C%20Lok%20Sangeet%20Shala%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20empowering%20young%20artists%20from%20folk%20communities%20to%20learn%20and%20celebrate%20their%20cultural%20identity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F375518%2Fgovind-bhati-sharon-lok-sangeet-shala-rajasthan-folk-music-jaisalmer-jodhpur-netflix-mismatched-mehman%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JEE%202025%20Now%20Allows%20Three%20Attempts%20%E2%80%93%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20Topper%E2%80%99s%20Guide%20To%20Make%20the%20Most%20of%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20update%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297383%2Fmumbai-ojas-maheshwari-with-hearing-impairment-tops-iit-jee-advanced-shares-strategy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJEE%20Advanced%20aspirants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Kanpur%20has%20announced%20that%2C%20starting%20in%202025%2C%20students%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20attempt%20the%20prestigious%20exam%20three%20times%20over%20three%20consecutive%20years.%20This%20marks%20a%20vital%20change%20from%20the%20earlier%20limit%20of%20two%20attempts%20in%20two%20consecutive%20years%2C%20which%20had%20been%20the%20standard%20for%20many%20years.%20It%20also%20gives%20students%20an%20additional%20chance%20to%20secure%20admission%20into%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20engineering%20colleges%2C%20the%20IITs.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20potential%20to%20turn%20opportunities%20into%20success%20is%20best%20exemplified%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334571%2Fkalpit-veerwal-jee-main-topper-launches-education-startup-iit-bombay-placement-package%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKalpit%20Veerwal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20inspiring%20success%20stories%20of%20JEE%20Mains.%20The%20first%20student%20to%20ever%20score%20a%20perfect%20360%2F360%20in%20the%20exam%2C%20Kalpit%E2%80%99s%20achievement%20not%20only%20earned%20him%20the%20All%20India%20Rank%201%20(AIR%201)%20in%20JEE%20Mains%202017%2C%20but%20also%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20a%20remarkable%20career.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20computer%20science%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%20in%202021%2C%20Kalpit%20went%20on%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20investor%2C%20leading%20his%20successful%20startup%20AcadBoost%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20online%20education%2C%20software%2C%20and%20email%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EA