ass%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20shackles%20of%20bonded%20labour%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayam%20%3Cem%3EAkka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%98elder%20sister%E2%80%99%20in%20Tamil%2C%20a%20term%20affectionately%20used%20by%20her%20team%20and%20community)%20was%20born%20into%20a%20family%20bound%20by%20bonded%20labour.%20She%20occasionally%20speaks%20courageously%20about%20the%20indignities%20of%20her%20early%20years%2C%20recalling%20tasks%20assigned%20to%20Dalit%20women%20and%20girls%20%E2%80%94%20including%20washing%20menstrual%20clothes%20for%20influential%20households%20where%20her%20father%20served%20as%20a%20bonded%20labourer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnwilling%20to%20continue%20a%20life%20of%20indignity%20and%20determined%20to%20break%20this%20cycle%20of%20intergenerational%20exploitation%2C%20she%20founded%20Salem%20People%20Trust%20(SPT).%20Since%202007%2C%20SPT%20has%20rescued%20and%20rehabilitated%20376%20bonded%20labourers%2C%20helped%201%2C372%20children%20return%20to%20school%20free%20from%20bonded%20labour%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20advocate%20for%20child%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20our%20initial%20focus%20was%20on%20ending%20bonded%20labour%2C%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20have%20freed%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20those%20affected%2C%20with%20their%20children%20now%20attending%20school.%20Our%20board%20members%20and%20staff%20are%20chosen%20from%20former%20bonded%20labourers%20and%20others%20with%20lived%20experiences%2C%20including%20child%20labour%20and%20the%20pressures%20of%20sex-selective%20abortion.%20We%20believe%20those%20who%20have%20lived%20through%20these%20challenges%20are%20best%20positioned%20to%20serve%20as%20community%20organisers%20and%20leaders.%20Their%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20allows%20us%20to%20effectively%20address%20the%20needs%20and%20bring%20meaningful%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20with%20flexible%20funding%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20often%20overlook%20that%20NGOs%20and%20their%20leaders%20need%20support%20to%20sustain%20their%20invaluable%20work.%20Office%20infrastructure%2C%20staff%20medical%20insurance%2C%20well-being%2C%20and%20capacity-building%20all%20demand%20investment%20beyond%20traditional%20community%20programmes%20to%20empower%20them%20to%20continue%20their%20efforts%20sustainably%20and%20without%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20flexible%20funding%20enables%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20with%20flexible%20support%20from%20the%20Rebuild%20India%20Fund%2C%20Jayam%20%3Cem%3EAkka%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20not%20only%20supporting%2010%20fellows%20to%20teach%20in%20five%20schools%20and%20organising%2020%20children%E2%80%99s%20collectives%20that%20impact%20over%202%2C500%20children%2C%20but%20she%E2%80%99s%20also%20able%20to%20make%20crucial%20investments%20in%20her%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2014%20years%20of%20grassroots%20work%20across%2045%20villages%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20she%20has%20purchased%20a%20laptop%2C%20desk%2C%20and%20chairs%20%E2%80%94%20marking%20a%20milestone%20in%20her%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20journey%20toward%20essential%20office%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSalem-People-Trust-1730979987.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jayam%20Akka%20in%20her%20newly%20built%20office%20in%20Salem%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSalem-People-Trust-1730979987.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSalem-People-Trust-1730979987-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c