0Over%201M%20Indian%20Inmates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20we%20will%20make%20it%20out%20of%20here%20one%20day.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20we%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20lose%20hope.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20(name%20changed%20on%20request)%2C%20a%20convict%20at%20a%20Ghaziabad%20prison%2C%20could%20often%20be%20heard%20boosting%20the%20morale%20of%20his%20fellow%20inmates.%20Most%20of%20them%20had%20given%20up%2C%20presuming%20they%20would%20be%20confined%20to%20prison%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20their%20lives.%20But%20Akshay%20would%20not%20accept%20this.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20get%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20would%20coax%20them%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20need%20to%20have%20something%20to%20show%20for%20our%20time%20spent%20here.%20So%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20get%20to%20work.%E2%80%9D%20His%20fellow%20inmates%20would%20cling%20to%20these%20words%20of%20encouragement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Akshay%2C%20the%20group%20would%20head%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F303942%2Famazon-future-engineer-programme-helps-teachers-students-learn-coding-computer-science-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesignated%20computer%20centre%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20jail%20quarters%2C%20where%20Word%2C%20Excel%2C%20and%20the%20basics%20of%20typing%20would%20occupy%20them%20for%20the%20next%20few%20hours.%20These%20masterclasses%20were%20brought%20to%20them%20by%20the%20Delhi-based%20India%20Vision%20Foundation%2C%20which%2C%20for%20three%20decades%2C%20has%20aimed%20its%20programmes%20at%20rehabilitating%20and%20reintegrating%20incarcerated%20individuals%20into%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20founder%2C%20Dr%20Kiran%20Bedi%2C%20the%20first%20woman%20IPS%20(Indian%20Police%20Service)%20officer%2C%20launched%20the%20foundation%20with%20the%20prize%20money%20from%20her%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20(1994).%20Through%20a%20host%20of%20programmes%2C%20the%20non-profit%20has%20been%20championing%20reforms%20in%20the%20prison%20system%2C%20both%20among%20inmates%20and%20officers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIndia-Vision-Foundation-prison-system-reforms-1730725101.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Kiran%20Bedi%20started%20the%20India%20Vision%20Foundation%20to%20bring%20reforms%20into%20the%20prison%20system%20in%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIndia-Vision-Foundation-prison-system-reforms-1730725101.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIndia-Vision-Foundation-prison-system-reforms-1730725101-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIndia-Vision-Foundation-prison-system-reforms-1730725101-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIndia-Vision-Foundation-prison-system-reforms-1730725101-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIndia-Vision-Foundation-prison-system-reforms-1730725101-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-373918%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Kiran%20Bedi%20started%20the%20India%20Vision%20Foundation%20to%20bring%20reforms%20to%20the%20prison%20system%20in%20India%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20current%20beneficiary%20count%20stands%20at%20a%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20initiatives%20spanning%20over%20a%20hundred%20prisons%20in%20India%2C%20the%20foundation%20is%20advocating%20change%20one%20grassr